				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Canh-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-ni%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-x1HY9Hmqz-E6-xMz9JnWwA">Canh Tuất niên chế - 庚戌年製</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/D%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BB%AD-Nghi%E1%BB%85m-%C4%91%E1%BA%B3ng-s%C6%A1/poem-OhDjdRxW8JN7rWvEJWQRVw">Dữ tử Nghiễm đẳng sơ - 與子儼等疏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/%C4%90%C3%A0o-hoa-nguy%C3%AAn-k%C3%BD/poem-M9lemd9pQXAQfGzmHL9Ynw">Đào hoa nguyên ký - 桃花源記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-t%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%8Dc-qu%C3%A1n/poem-eO2h4-Q2uEZY7HdsQAKaQw">Đề tân học quán - 題新學館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-H%E1%BB%93-b%C3%BAt-ph%C3%BA/poem-zjv_6tPCykW3dsLfeEVU1g">Đổng Hồ bút phú - 董狐筆賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-k%E1%BB%B9-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-bPfX0CCiakgX1jD7f9KqFA">Đồng Tước kỹ kỳ 1 - 銅雀妓其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/author-_ZqxSvkbsUwNbnMEINI85Q">Vương Bột</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/Ho%C3%A0ng-L%C4%83ng-mi%E1%BA%BFu-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-soG-t-qR_K6k8q7MDj884w">Hoàng Lăng miếu kỳ 1 - 黃陵廟其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/author-zIVIj-WVByE189TCoytv8g">Lý Quần Ngọc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Thi%C3%AAn-Du-qu%C3%A1n-V%E1%BA%A1n-Phong-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-QW3SIuM9zjSd3AwL0YuRog">Thiên Du quán Vạn Phong đình - 天遊觀萬峰亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/Thi%C3%AAn-H%C6%B0ng-tr%E1%BA%A5n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zfk8LWGL0mEgBMai1LRNPA">Thiên Hưng trấn phú - 天興鎮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/author-UlfffDmWp64stOugtjh9rQ">Nguyễn Bá Thông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
